{"title":"陇南春","authors":["高平"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陇南春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陇南的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倚在两种色调的衔接处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北面有黄衬衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南面有花裙子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她穿戴如江南女子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心却爱怜黄土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄用十指把翠绿向北弹去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陇南的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫过古蜀道上的铁路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收藏李白的想象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安抚杜甫的足迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她采累了一路的美丽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头枕麦积山，脚伸九寨沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微张着口  吐出酒的香气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春，陶醉了陇南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可想起“得陇望蜀”的成语？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜀也在望陇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有别的，都是春意。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}